<h3>First look at Gungrave Gore Blood Heat</h3>
<p>A remake of the 2002 PS2 game, today we got a first look at Gungrave Gore Blood Heat - a third-person action shooter with extravagant gore. It's been built in Unreal Engine 5 for improved visuals and will be released on Xbox Series X/S, as well as PS5 and Steam.</p>

