<p>Arc System Works is updating the classic beat 'em up Double Dragon - here we saw its story mode as well as a load of missions and episodic stories in its Extra Mode. It's out on 23rd October across Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PS4, PS5, Switch, PC (Steam, Epic).</p>

