<p>Bruce Lee is today joining <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/hitman-world-of-assassination">Hitman World of Assassination</a> as the latest Elusive Target. He's not actually a target, though, but an ally, so you'll need to neutralise anyone else attempting to kill him. The update is available on all platforms from today until 20th November.</p>

